Package: dxcluster-scraper
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-psycopg2, python3-dotenv, systemd, dxcluster-database (>= 1.0.0)
Description: DX Cluster Data Scraper Service
 This package provides a systemd service for continuously monitoring
 DX cluster feeds and storing spot data in a PostgreSQL database.
 .
  * Socket-based DX cluster monitoring (no deprecated telnetlib)
  * Automatic data parsing and storage
  * Systemd service integration
  * Production-ready configuration
 .
 The service connects to DX cluster servers, parses incoming spot
 data, and stores it in the database for analysis and web display.